1:29:40.501 --> 1:29:42.544
That'll be all, thank you, Mr Singh.

1:30:04.566 --> 1:30:06.568
I wonder, Mr Wakeling,

1:30:06.860 --> 1:30:12.366
if I may now turn to matters
you may consider more personal.

1:30:13.951 --> 1:30:17.162
I have no wish
to belittle our playground...

1:30:17.788 --> 1:30:21.166
but I put it to you that it was,
all the same...

1:30:21.333 --> 1:30:22.793
a small thing.

1:30:23.293 --> 1:30:26.213
And that it will, before long...

1:30:26.380 --> 1:30:28.882
go the way of most small things.

1:30:31.260 --> 1:30:33.846
It may fall into disrepair,

1:30:34.012 --> 1:30:37.975
or be superseded
by some grander scheme.

1:30:39.601 --> 1:30:41.270
To speak plainly,

1:30:41.436 --> 1:30:45.899
